# LegalRAG v2.0 — Complete Legal Practice Management + AI Platform

Transform the current legal search tool into a **role-based AI assistant** with case management, client management, and intelligent legal analysis — **100% free, Ollama-powered**.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a significant redesign. The current single-pane chat interface will become a **multi-dashboard application** with three distinct role-based views. All existing RAG and search functionality is preserved and enhanced.

> [!WARNING]
> Files to be **deleted**: [implementation_plan.md.resolved](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/implementation_plan.md.resolved), [walkthrough.md.resolved](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/walkthrough.md.resolved), [tests/test_output.txt](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/tests/test_output.txt) — these are stale artifacts from the initial build.

