## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend — Role-Based Dashboards"]
        LP[Login/Role Selector]
        JD[Judge Dashboard]
        AD[Advocate Dashboard]
        PD[Public Dashboard]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend["FastAPI Backend"]
        API[API Routes]
        RAG[RAG Engine]
        CM[Case Manager]
        CLM[Client Manager]
    end
    
    subgraph Storage["Local Storage — 100% Free"]
        VS[(ChromaDB Vectors)]
        DB[(SQLite DB)]
        FS[File Storage]
    end
    
    subgraph AI["Local AI — Ollama"]
        LLM[Mistral / LLaMA]
        EMB[Sentence Transformer]
    end
    
    LP --> JD & AD & PD
    JD & AD & PD --> API
    API --> RAG & CM & CLM
    RAG --> VS & LLM & EMB
    CM & CLM --> DB
    API --> FS
```

---

## Three Role-Based Dashboards

### 1. Judge Dashboard
| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Today's Docket** | Cases scheduled for today with status badges |
| **Case Manager** | Full case lifecycle: parties, dates, status, hearings |
| **Law Search + Summarizer** | Search any Indian law → get IRAC summary with bullet points |
| **Case History Retrieval** | Who won, why, reasoning — for any act/section |
| **Case Documents** | Upload/view case papers, orders, applications |
| **Case-Specific RAG** | Ask AI about a specific case using its uploaded documents |
| **Notes & Orders** | Draft notes and orders with AI assistance |

### 2. Advocate Dashboard
| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Client Manager** | Add clients, track their cases, contact info |
| **Payment Tracker** | Record fees, payments, outstanding balances |
| **Case Research** | Find supporting arguments, precedents, counter-arguments |
| **Argument Builder** | AI analyzes case papers and builds structured arguments |
| **Section Analysis** | Deep-dive into specific sections with case history |
| **Case Paper RAG** | Upload opposing party's papers → AI finds weaknesses |
| **My Cases** | All active cases with status, next hearing, client |

### 3. Public Dashboard
| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Situation Describer** | Describe your problem in plain language |
| **Evidence Upload** | Upload documents, photos, witness statements |
| **AI Legal Guidance** | Get plain-language explanation of your rights |
| **Relevant Laws** | See which laws apply to your situation |
| **Case History** | Similar past cases and their outcomes |
| **Next Steps** | Practical advice — what to do next, where to go |

