### Database — New Tables

#### [MODIFY] [database.py](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/backend/database.py)

Add new tables:

| Table | Purpose | Key Columns |
|-------|---------|-------------|
| `cases` | Case management | case_number, title, parties, court, judge, status, next_hearing, created_at |
| `hearings` | Hearing schedule | case_id, date, time, court_room, status, notes |
| `case_documents` | Per-case documents | case_id, doc_id, filename, doc_type, file_path |
| `clients` | Advocate's clients | name, phone, email, address, notes |
| `client_cases` | Client ↔ Case link | client_id, case_id, role (petitioner/respondent) |
| `payments` | Fee tracking | client_id, case_id, amount, date, status, description |
| `case_notes` | Judge/advocate notes | case_id, user_role, content, created_at |

