### API Routes — New Endpoints

#### [NEW] [cases.py](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/backend/routes/cases.py)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/cases` | Create a new case |
| `GET` | `/api/cases` | List all cases (with filters) |
| `GET` | `/api/cases/{id}` | Get case details |
| `PUT` | `/api/cases/{id}` | Update case status/details |
| `DELETE` | `/api/cases/{id}` | Delete a case |
| `POST` | `/api/cases/{id}/documents` | Upload case document |
| `GET` | `/api/cases/{id}/documents` | List case documents |
| `POST` | `/api/cases/{id}/notes` | Add a case note |
| `GET` | `/api/cases/{id}/notes` | Get case notes |
| `POST` | `/api/cases/{id}/rag` | RAG query on case documents |

#### [NEW] [clients.py](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/backend/routes/clients.py)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/clients` | Add a client |
| `GET` | `/api/clients` | List clients |
| `GET` | `/api/clients/{id}` | Client details with cases |
| `PUT` | `/api/clients/{id}` | Update client info |
| `DELETE` | `/api/clients/{id}` | Remove a client |

#### [NEW] [payments.py](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/backend/routes/payments.py)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/payments` | Record a payment |
| `GET` | `/api/payments` | List payments (with filters) |
| `GET` | `/api/payments/summary` | Payment summary / outstanding |

#### [MODIFY] [query.py](file:///c:/Users/ROG/Downloads/legal_ai_assistant/backend/routes/query.py)

- Add `/api/query/summarize-law` — Structured law summary with subheadings
